{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"67680-wisane","title":"ውሣኔ","description":"A village takes a decision together to change their lives for the better.","language":"Amharic","langCode":"am","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mezemir Girma"],"illustrators":["Vusi  Malindi"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/67680-wisane"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106408/size3/1810d196f828b94b51312fbbe19e1392.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106408/size6/1810d196f828b94b51312fbbe19e1392.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90909/size6/649abe138b0754cea90fe1e5b37865ef.jpg","text":"መንደሬ ብዙ ችግር ነበረባት። ውሃ\nከቦኖ ለመቅዳት ረጅም ሰልፍ\nእንሰለፍ ነበር።","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90916/size6/b32ad7caaebb3a1b63990f4a5b972029.jpg","text":"በሌሎች ሰዎች የሚሰጠንን ምግብ\nእንጠብቅ ነበር።","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90914/size6/5d622ce10047f60cf06face040796337.jpg","text":"ሌባ ፍራቻ ቤቶቻችንን በጊዜ እንዘጋነበር።","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90911/size6/545d2d962e9802f126e9f5f78d4c135a.jpg","text":"ብዙ ልጆች ትምህርታቸውን ያቋርጡ\nነበር።","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90913/size6/30597595e3bba307b74e54865f835f8f.jpg","text":"ወጣት ሴቶች በሌሎች መንደሮች\nውስጥ በሰራተኝነት ያገለግሉ ነበር።","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90915/size6/7d206932be27df73daf1b578aca388f5.jpg","text":"ግማሾቹ ወንዶች ልጆች በየሰፈሩ\nእየዞሩ ሲውሉ፤ ሌሎቹ ደግሞ በሰው\nማሳ ላይ ያገለግሉ ነበር።","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90917/size6/7089a1665e5b94c7c18fcfa4396c7690.jpg","text":"ነፋስ በነፈሰ ቁጥር ቆሻሻ ወረቀት\nበየአጥሩና በየዛፉ ላይ ይንጠለጠል\nነበር።","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90912/size6/ad71793535db380123bc70820af9d2f7.jpg","text":"ሰዎችን በጥንቃቄ ጉድለት የተጣለ\nብርጭቆ ይቆርጣቸው ነበር።","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90910/size6/102138e2e04c6edaad1211fe8d99f4fe.jpg","text":"አንድ ቀን ውሃው ቆመና የውሃ\nመያዣዎቻችን ባዶ ቀሩ።","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90918/size6/64bcbbd430ec3517bd16550388bd2b85.jpg","text":"አባቴ ሰዎች በመንደር ስብሰባ ላይ\nእንዲገኙ ለመቀስቀስ ከቤት ቤት\nዞረ።","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90919/size6/c288bf3f023d69962ac81e2d4e034fb7.jpg","text":"ሰዎች ከአንድ ትልቅ ዛፍ ስር\nተቀምጠው ያዳምጡ ጀመር።","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90920/size6/3d7e1ebecd564debe8960477dbea2563.jpg","text":"አባቴ ተነስቶ ‹‹እነዚህን\nችግሮቻችንን ለመፍታት በጋራ\nመስራት ይኖርብናል›› አለ።","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90921/size6/801a10f7518c2018eaa33d81560af470.jpg","text":"ግንድ ላይ የተቀመጠው የስምንት ዓመቱ ዓመቱ ጁማ ‹‹እኔ በማጽዳት እራዳለሁ›› ሲል ተናገረ።","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90923/size6/7bf60142cd090b366bbdff029b4fc638.jpg","text":"አንዲት ሴትዮም ‹‹ሴቶቹ ከኔ ጋር\nዝሪት ላይ መሰማራት ይችላሉ››\nአሉ።","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90925/size6/229b1a3aec0c2e353b5410e8dc871556.jpg","text":"ሌላ ሰውዬ ተነሳና ‹‹እኛ ወንዶቹ\nጉድጓድ መቆፈር እንችላለን›› አለ።","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90927/size6/0636d10e9a730c7e6676dfc39659fc9b.jpg","text":"ሁላችንም በአንድ ድምጽ\n‹‹ህይወታችንን መቀየር\nይኖርብናል›› በማለት ጮህን።\nከዚያች ቀን ጀምረን ችግሮቻችንን\nለመፍታት አብረን እንሰራ ጀመር።","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":147}}